OL,3,CMum who flew to Ibiza while schoolboy
OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FA mum of a 12-year-old who flew to
OL,8,FIbiza instead of accompanying her son
OL,9,Fto court over riot charges has been
OL,10,Freprimanded by a judge - who called
OL,11,Fher son's behaviour "feral".
OL,13,FThe 30-year-old single mother, who was
OL,14,Fsummoned to court alongside the boy -
OL,15,Fone of Britain's youngest criminals
OL,16,Finvolved in the summer riots - was
OL,17,Ffined #1,200 the same cost as her
OL,18,Fholiday to the Spanish island.
