OL,3,CMum who flew to Ibiza while schoolboy
OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FAfter an hour-long hearing, District
OL,8,FJudge Joanne Hirst also ordered the
OL,9,Fmother to take part in a six-month
OL,10,Fparenting course telling her: "You
OL,11,Fknow it's approximately the same cost
OL,12,Fas your holiday to Ibiza."
OL,14,FThe judge told the youngster, at
OL,15,FManchester Magistrates Court, he had
OL,16,Fbeen involved in "the worst type of
OL,17,Fferal behaviour in our country".
