OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe court was told the boy's mother
OL,8,Fhad decided to fly abroad for a five-
OL,9,Fday sunshine break, the day before he
OL,10,Fwas due to appear in court at the
OL,11,Fbeginning of September for sentence
OL,12,Fafter admitting two counts of violent
OL,13,Fdisorder.
OL,15,FThe boy had been accompanied by his
OL,16,Funcle but Judge Hirst said the
OL,17,Fmother's actions left her, "frankly
OL,18,Fastonished" and at the hearing on 2
OL,19,FSeptember, said she would summon the
OL,20,Fwoman to court to explain herself.
