OL,7,FIn court, the judge asked the mother:
OL,8,F"Can you explain your point of view?"
OL,10,FThe mother said she spoke with her
OL,11,Fsolicitor and the Youth Justice team,
OL,12,Fadding: "It was not put to me how much
OL,13,FI needed to be there. Each one said,
OL,14,F'Is there an appropriate adult?' My
OL,15,Fbrother ` which is why I went on
OL,16,Fholiday."
OL,18,FAfter speaking to his mother, the
OL,19,Fcourt was shown video footage of his
OL,20,Foffences.
