OL,3,CMum who flew to Ibiza while schoolboy
OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe boy had ridden his bike in front
OL,8,Fof the bus, forcing it to stop, as it
OL,9,Fpassed a protest outside a hotel
OL,10,Fhousing asylum seekers in Manchester
OL,11,Fon 31 July.
OL,13,FThe boy then kicked the bus as a mob
OL,14,Fattacked the vehicle and the driver of
OL,15,Fthe bus, leaving passengers, one a
OL,16,Fresident of the hotel, terrified.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
