OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FDays later on 3 August the boy,
OL,8,Fwearing a balaclava, was in Manchester
OL,9,Fcity centre, where he knocked over
OL,10,Fshelves in a Sainsbury's store as it
OL,11,Fwas looted then kicked the glass door
OL,12,Fof a vape shop as others tried to
OL,13,Fbreak into the premises.
OL,15,FDozens of towns and cities saw
OL,16,Fviolence erupt following the killing
OL,17,Fof three young girls at a Taylor Swift-
OL,18,Fthemed dance class in Southport on 29
OL,19,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
