OL,3,CMum who flew to Ibiza while schoolboy
OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FCatherine Baird, defending, told the
OL,8,Fcourt the youngster had no previous
OL,9,Fconvictions, adding: "This is a child.
OL,10,FHe simply got wrapped up, surrounded
OL,11,Fby peers, many of them were adults.
OL,12,FCustody would do more harm than good."
OL,14,FThe judge asked him directly about his
OL,15,Fbehaviour.
OL,17,F"It's horrible. I'm just worried that
OL,18,FI might get, like... jailed."
