OL,4,Cson in court ordered to pay
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FShe told the mixed-race youngster the
OL,8,Fhotel was for asylum seekers and asked
OL,9,Fif he had ever suffered racism and how
OL,10,Fit made him feel.
OL,12,F"One time. Really sad."
OL,14,FAsked what he would say to the asylum
OL,15,Fseekers, he replied: "I would not know
OL,16,Fexactly what to say, but I would say
OL,17,Fsorry."
